-- Stephen Cunningham
-- 2010-06-22T07:18:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-22/bg-slides-as-much-as-2-6-in-london-after-goldman-sachs-downgrades-stock.html

          
          
             BG Group Plc fell as much as 2.6
percent in London trading after being cut to “neutral” from
“buy” at Goldman Sachs Group Inc.  
          
          


  


        